		<b>Comment By Dick Hart, 1-05-09</b>
		<p>Obscenity & blasphemy!  Missed the Colorado Gathering again!  Would someone please put me on the mailing list, e-mail or postal, and notify me of the 2009 Gathering?  My second book of cowboy/country poetry, Revenge of the Rexall Wrangler, has just been published, and is available on Amazon.com and Barnes& Noble.com.  You can order my first book, Rhymes of a Rexall Wrangler, from me at 7132 Cordova Drive, Cheyenne, WY 82009; $8.95 plus a dollar shipping & handling and, if you live in Wyoming, 45 cents sales tax.  I'd give you a sample, but the box is too small.</p>
		
